Set consists of most variations.  Missing is the Hoblitzell no stats and the Wilhelm suffered. Set put together over a couple of years.  Contains cards that I would grade as poor to excellent. Some cards are trimmed and some have some paper loss. I have scanned entire set.  All cards are in sleeves inside an SGC frame.  The tape is hoding the cards to the frame. I would like to sell entire set, not individually.  Asking 7K
